dcterms:description: The Davis dataset includes interactions between a subset of selectivity assays from a kinase protein family and a set of inhibitors, which were measured using the dissociation constant (Kd) across 442 unique proteins and 68 unique drugs.
dcterms:title: Davis kinase dataset

dcterms:description: The KIBA dataset was designed to cover the bioactivity of specific kinase inhibitors from various studies, which were combined to include interactions based on Ki, Kd and IC50 values.
